Description: Picks the suitable cell types in spatial 
    transcriptomics data using Lasso regression. The package includes curated reference 
    gene expression profiles for human and mouse cell types, facilitating immediate application 
    to common spatial transcriptomics datasets. Additionally, users can input custom reference 
    data to support tissue- or experiment-specific analyses.
